==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Keeled
<hw>Keeled</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Keel-shaped; having a longitudinal prominence on
the back; <as>as, a <ex>keeled</ex> leaf</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Having a median ridge; carinate;
<as>as, a <ex>keeled</ex> scale</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Keeler</ent>⟦br⟧
